AS A LIQUID AND AS A FROZEN SOLID SHEET OF ICE WHICH NEVER GIVES IN TO THE TEMPERATURE EFFECTS BELOW IT BECAUSE THE OUTER SHELL OF THE BUBBLED DOME IS AT THE ABSOLUTE LOWEST TEMPERATURE THAT EXISTS! AND IT WILL ALWAYS REMAIN FROZEN SOLID IN THE THRID FORM OF NITROGEN AS AN ICE WHICH CONSTANTLY FEEDS MORE LIQUID NITROGEN TO THE BUBBLED DOME, ANYTIME THE BUBBLED DOME BEGINS TO THAW ON THE INSIDE THIS DOMED FIRMAMENT ALSO CREATES OTHER GASES BEING FORMED FROM NATURAL CAUSES BEING EITHER FROM INSIDE THE EARTH OR FROM LIVING BREATHING CREATURES AND PLANTS CAUSING THE DOME TO EXPAND UPWARDS WITH THE INCREASING ATMOSPHERIC PRESSURES!
